Java Tools (Jokp)

Source code for tools used to improve code quality / styling

TabsToWhitespace.java (requires Java 7)
 + Reclusively converts all tabs to four whitespaces in ONLY java & xml files
 + Removes trailing whitespaces
 + Removes '\r' left from Windows saved files

usage examples:
# compile the tool
javac TabsToWhitespace.java

# to reclusively convert a single directory
java TabsToWhitespace ~/path/to/directory/

# to reclusively convert multiple directories
java TabsToWhitespace ~/path/to/directory/ ~/path/to/another/directory/

# to convert only one file
java TabsToWhitespace ~/or/path/to/single/file.java

# to convert multiple directories and multiple single files
java TabsToWhitespace ~/path/to/directory/ ~/path/to/another/directory/ \
    ~/path/to/SomeClass.java ~/path/to/AnotherClass.java

